trans-unit.source: Defines the interaction between [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] applications that are hosting interoperation content and interpreted by the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] executable, and a host supplied error page.
